   neighborhood context were incorporated. Three models-K-Nearest Neighbors
   (KNN), Multi-Layer Perceptron (MLP), and Light Gradient Boosting Machine
   (LightGBM)-were evaluated. LightGBM outperformed others, showing the
   benefits of integrating remote sensing with contextual data. The model
   achieved strong regression performance with
