   Prasad, Pankaj, Mahapurusha Srimanta Sankaradeva Viswavidyalaya, Dept Geog, Geoinformat Div, Nagaon 782001, Assam, India.
   Jeganathan, C., Sarala Birla Univ, Ranchi 835103, Jharkhand, India.
   Das, Pallab Kumar; Mukherjee, Indrajit, Birla Inst Technol Mesra, Dept Comp Sci \& Engn, Ranchi 835215, Jharkhand, India.
   Agrawal, Akhilesh, Reg Off, Indian Bur Mines, Jabalpur 482002, Madhya Pradesh, India.},
DOI = {10.1007/s10668-026-07528-6},
