   Huang, Chunlin, Lanzhou Jiaotong Univ, Fac Geomat, Lanzhou 730070, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.5194/essd-18-1995-2026},
Keywords-Plus = {GRAIN-SIZE; LANDSAT; RETRIEVAL; ALGORITHM; AREA; PERFORMANCE;
