   Faqeih, Khadeijah Yahya; Alamri, Somayah Moshrif; Alamery, Eman Rafi, Princess Nourah bint Abdulrahman Univ, Coll Humanities \& Social Sci, Dept Geog \& Environm Sustainabil, Riyadh, Saudi Arabia.
   Utkina, Aleksandra O., RUDN Univ, Inst Environm Engn, Moscow, Russia.
   Tariq, Aqil, Mississippi State Univ, Coll Forest Resources, Dept Wildlife Fisheries \& Aquaculture, Starkville, MS 39762 USA.},
DOI = {10.1002/ldr.70497},
