   Bulto, Gamtesa Olika; Wedajo, Gizachew Kabite, Entoto Observ \& Res Ctr EORC, Space Sci \& Geospatial Inst, Dept Remote Sensing, PO Box 33679, Addis Ababa, Ethiopia.
   Bulto, Gamtesa Olika, Addis Ababa Univ, PO Box 1176, Addis Ababa, Ethiopia.
   Bulto, Gamtesa Olika, Wollega Univ, Fac Resource Management \& Econ, Dept Nat Resources Management, Shambu Campus,PO Box 38, Shambu, Ethiopia.
