   Chala, Desalegn, Univ Oslo, Nat Hist Museum, Oslo, Norway.
   Gemeda, Dessalegn Obsi, Jimma Univ, Coll Agr \& Vet Med, Dept Nat Resource Management, PO Box 307, Jimma, Ethiopia.
   Gemeda, Dessalegn Obsi, Policy \& Strategy Lab, Social Ecol Syst, Dutse 720101, Nigeria.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.tfp.2026.101218},
Article-Number = {101218},
Keywords = {Invasive species mapping; Vachellia drepanolobium; Selective ensemble
   modeling; Ecological niche modeling; Sentinel-2; Remote sensing; Savanna
   ecosystem management},
