   Fan, Zenghui, Cent South Univ, Sch Geosci \& Info Phys, Changsha, Peoples R China.
   Yu, Zhen, Nanjing Univ Informat Sci \& Technol, Inst Ecol, Sch Appl Meteorol, Nanjing, Jiangsu, Peoples R China.
   Tian, Feng; Mao, Feiyue, Wuhan Univ, State Key Lab Informat Engn Surveying Mapping \& Re, Wuhan 430079, Hubei, Peoples R China.
   Gong, Wei, Wuhan Univ, Elect Informat Sch, Luoyu Rd 129, Wuhan 430079, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.jag.2026.105179},
