   Gole, Tadesse Woldemariam, Environm \& Coffee Forest Forum, Addis Ababa, Ethiopia.
   Chala, Desalegn, Univ Oslo, Nat Hist Museum, Oslo, Norway.
   Gemeda, Dessalegn Obsi, Jimma Univ, Coll Agr \& Vet Med, Dept Nat Resource Management, POB 307, Jimma, Ethiopia.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.indic.2026.101184},
EarlyAccessDate = {FEB 2026},
