   Yu, Yingying, CSIRO Environm, Ecosci Precinct, Dutton Pk, Qld 4102, Australia.
   Shahadat, Mustafa Kamal, Bangladesh Agr Res Inst, Onfarm Res Div, Khulna, Bangladesh.
