   Wang, Hongfei; Zhang, Ziyou; Jiang, Zhekai; Wei, Qi; Yi, Weijie; Chen, Tao; Ma, Junwei, China Univ Geosci, Three Gorges Res Ctr Geohazards, Minist Educ, Wuhan 430074, Peoples R China.
   Deng, Chuhan, Tianjin Univ, Sch Civil Engn, Tianjin 300072, Peoples R China.
