   Suwanlee, Savittri Ratanopad; Keawsomsee, Surasak; Kasa, Kemin; Som-ard, Jaturong, Mahasarakham Univ, Earth Observat Technol Land \& Agr Dev Res Unit, Maha Sarakham 44150, Thailand.
   Ninsawat, Sarawut, Asian Inst Technol, Sch Engn \& Technol, Remote Sensing \& GIS, Klongluang 12120, Pathum Thani, Thailand.
