   Chen, Minghao; Ren, Yan; Zhang, Lei, Lanzhou Univ, Collaborat Innovat Ctr Western Ecol Safety, Lanzhou 730000, Peoples R China.
   Chen, Minghao; Ren, Yan; Tang, Weiqi; Liang, Jiening; Cao, Xianjie; Tian, Pengfei; Zhang, Lei, Lanzhou Univ, Minist Educ, Coll Atmospher Sci, Key Lab Semiarid Climate Change, Lanzhou 730000, Peoples R China.
   Zhang, Hongsheng, Peking Univ, Sch Phys, Dept Atmospher \& Ocean Sci, Lab Climate \& Ocean Atmosphere Studies, Beijing 100081, Peoples R China.
