   Management},
Journal = {EURASIAN SOIL SCIENCE},
Year = {2026},
Volume = {59},
Number = {2},
Month = {JAN 30},
Abstract = {Soil salinization disrupts ecosystem material and energy cycling,
   leading to agricultural resource wastage, ecological degradation, and
   economic losses. This study developed soil salinity prediction models
   using 1247 samples from China's Kashgar Oasis through five machine
   learning methods-Ordinary Least Squares (OLS), Backpropagation Neural
   Network (BP), Random Forest (RF), Support Vector Machine (SVM), and
   Extreme Learning Machine (ELM)-integrated with multi-source
   environmental variables. Dominant ions (Cl-, Na+,
