   Laamrani, Ahmed, Univ Guelph, Dept Geog Environm \& Geomatics, Guelph, ON N1G 2W1, Canada.
   Whalen, Joann K., UM6P, Ctr Sustainable Soil Sci C3S, Ben Guerir 43150, Morocco.
   Whalen, Joann K., McGill Univ, Dept Nat Resource Sci, Ste Anne De Bellevue, PQ H9X 3V9, Canada.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.rsase.2026.101896},
EarlyAccessDate = {JAN 2026},
