   Xie, Xiaowen; Dai, Zhijun; Wang, Riming; Wu, Tianliang; Hu, Baoqing; Liang, Xixing, Nanning Normal Univ, Key Lab Environm Change \& Resources Use Beibu Gulf, Minist Educ, Nanning 530001, Peoples R China.
