   Qin, Peng; Huang, Huabing; Wang, Jie; Xia, Yu; Liu, Xiangyu, Pengcheng Lab, Shenzhen 518066, Peoples R China.
   Cui, Yunxia, Hebei Agr Univ, Baoding 071000, Peoples R China.
   Chen, Shuang; Yuan, Shuai, Univ Hong Kong, Dept Geog, Hong Kong, Peoples R China.
   Li, Yumei, Beijing Technol \& Business Univ, Sch Math \& Stat, Beijing 100048, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.isprsjprs.2026.01.015},
EarlyAccessDate = {JAN 2026},
