   Man, Weidong; Li, Fuping, Hebei Ind Technol Inst Mine Ecol Remediat, Tangshan 063210, Peoples R China.
   Liu, Mingyue, Collaborat Innovat Ctr Green Dev \& Ecol Restorat M, Tangshan 063210, Peoples R China.},
