   Zhao, Hang, China Ctr Resources Satellite Data \& Applicat, Beijing 100094, Peoples R China.
   Xue, Yongan, Taiyuan Univ Technol, Coll Geol \& Surveying Engn, Taiyuan 030021, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1109/TGRS.2026.3668416},
