   Spatial resolution; Remote sensing; Satellites; Monitoring; Temperature
   sensors; DQ-1 satellite; extreme gradient boosting (XGBoost); improved
   sparrow search algorithm (ISSA); machine learning; retrieval; sea
   surface temperature (SST)},
