   Han, Wenting, Northwest A\&F Univ, Inst Water Saving Agr Arid Areas China, Yangling 712100, Peoples R China.
   Zhou, Zhenjiang, Zhejiang Univ, Coll Biosyst Engn \& Food Sci, Hangzhou 310058, Peoples R China.
   Zhou, Zhenjiang, Zhejiang Univ, Zhejiang Key Lab Intelligent Sensing \& Robot Agr, Hangzhou 310058, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1109/JSTARS.2026.3654635},
