Affiliation = {Jiang, CB (Corresponding Author), Hunan Univ Technol, Zhuzhou 412007, Peoples R China.
   Yan, Shixiong; Long, Yuannan; Deng, Bin; Huang, Zhiyong; Wang, Xinkui, Changsha Univ Sci \& Technol, Sch Hydraul \& Ocean Engn, Changsha 410114, Peoples R China.
