   Naboureh, Amin; Li, Ainong; Bian, Jinhu; Lei, Guangbin; Nan, Xi; Zhang, Zhengjian, Wanglang Mt Remote Sensing Observat \& Res Stn Sic, Mianyang, Peoples R China.
