   Ma, Gelilan; Zhao, Chuanwu; Wu, Hanyi; Gao, Yuan; Ren, Shoujia; Pan, Yaozhong, Beijing Normal Univ, Fac Geog Sci, State Key Lab Remote Sensing, Beijing 100875, Peoples R China.
