   Som-ard, J (Corresponding Author), Mahasarakham Univ, Fac Humanities \& Social Sci, Dept Geog, Maha Sarakham, Thailand.
   Qaisrani, Zahid Naeem; Mengal, Ali Nawaz, Balochistan Univ Informat Technol \& Management Sci, Fac Engn \& Architecture, Dept Chem Engn, Balochistan, Pakistan.
   Qaisrani, Zahid Naeem; Som-ard, Jaturong; Suwanlee, Savittri Ratanopad; Keawsomsee, Surasak, Mahasarakham Univ, Earth Observat Technol Land \& Agr Dev Res Unit, Maha Sarakham, Thailand.
