   Huang, Duan, East China Univ Technol, Sch Surveying \& Geoinformat Engn, Nanchang, Peoples R China.
   Chen, Zhiping, Jiangxi Geol \& Mineral Surveying \& Mapping Co Ltd, Jiangxi Nonlinear Geol Mineral Explorat \& Dev Inst, Nanchang, Peoples R China.
   Li, Hengkai, Jiangxi Univ Sci \& Technol, Jiangxi Prov Key Lab Water Ecol Conservat Headwate, Ganzhou, Jiangxi, Peoples R China.
