   Liao, Ming, Jiangxi Prov Nat Resources Cause Dev Ctr, Nanchang, Peoples R China.
   Liao, Ming, Jiangxi Prov Engn Res Ctr Surveying Mapping \& Geog, Nanchang, Peoples R China.},
