   Lian, Jie; Bai, Jian, Beijing Inst Remote Sensing Equipment, Beijing 100039, Peoples R China.
   Feng, Wei, Xidian Univ, Sch Informat Mech \& Sensing Engn, Xian 710071, Peoples R China.
