   Aengngam, Chalongrat; Engphorm, Panuwat, Natl Astron Res Inst Thailand, Chiang Mai 50180, Thailand.
   Utthapornnitchakul, Surapa, Prince Songkla Univ, Fac Sci \& Technol, Dept Sci, Pattani 94000, Thailand.
   Init, Sompop, Naresuan Univ, Fac Med Sci, Dept Biochem, Phitsanulok 65000, Thailand.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.rsci.2025.08.004},
