   Alsafadi, Karam, Xiamen Univ, Coll Environm \& Ecol, Key Lab Marine Environm Sci, Xiamen 361102, Peoples R China.
   Zhao, Gang, Northwest A\&F Univ, State Key Lab Soil Eros \& Dryland Farming Loess Pl, Yangling 712100, Peoples R China.
